query: SELECT g.id as gestor_id, v.id as volante_id, v.nome as volante_nome FROM gestores g LEFT JOIN volantes v ON v.gestorId = g.id INNER JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id WHERE u.email = 'mramorim78@gmail.com';
